				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">No need to modify the bot.php to get this to work in IGN.
<br />

<br />
The following plugin which was very quickly throw together will work just fine without any other tinkering under pluginmain, and it will also send out an alert to guildchat when cloaking can be enabled and disabled.
<br />

<br />
There are some additional variables set which are called from a separate plugin which will display current status aswell, but not included here.
<br />
If you do not use IRC, you probably should remove the ircsend calls, ive not tested this on a bot with IRC disabled.
<br />

<br />
(Yes i know its messy. It was quickly thrown together rather late at night and i havent bothered cleaning it up yet)
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
